desc: Some questions team members should ask themselves at the end of every day

questions.one: did I use my time effeciently?

questions.three: did I leverage all the resources available to me?

questions.four: What can I do differently today than yesterday?

questions.five: Do I feel like my role has an impact on the project?

questions.six: Am I good at giving/receiving feedback and colloborating with my team respectfully?
